MEDICAL USE DISCLAIMER:
This software is designed for healthcare professional use and educational 
demonstration purposes. It is NOT intended for direct patient diagnosis 
without medical professional oversight. All medical decisions generated by 
this system should be validated by qualified healthcare providers before 
implementation. The developers assume no responsibility for medical decisions 
made using this software.

HIPAA COMPLIANCE:
This software includes features for HIPAA compliance including PHI tokenization
and audit trails. However, users are responsible for ensuring their specific
implementation and deployment meets all applicable healthcare regulations.

CLINICAL VALIDATION:
While this software implements real NPUAP/EPUAP 2019 clinical guidelines,
it has not undergone clinical trials or FDA approval. It should be used as
a clinical decision support tool only, with final medical decisions made by
qualified healthcare professionals.

